for the QSO formation while t $_{sup}$, which is determined by the
efficiency of angular momentum transfer, is shorter than \~{}10$^{8}$
yr. The evolution of the QSO luminosity depends on the redshift z
$_{i}$ at which accretion onto a seed BH is initiated. In other
