abundance could exceed
x$_{H<SUB>2}$,cr</SUB>\~{}=3{\times}10$^{-3}$ by reactions of
H+e--{\gt}H$^{-}$+h{$\nu$} and H+H$^{-}$--{\gt}H$_{2}$+e.
The high-mass peak would then be O(10)M$_{solar}$.
}},
