the thermal gas due to a cosmic-ray driven acoustic instability. <BR
/>Methods: We perform hydrodynamic simulations to find solutions to the
time-dependent, one-dimensional two-fluid equations governing the
thermal fluid and cosmic-ray fluid. Source terms transferring energy
